message.body: Hey let's up sometime tomorrow or Friday for that dinner if you're free!

Also Sophie said she isn't totally happy with the card so this might be a good time for me to make that little logo I was thinking of and see if it might help at all. The card looks great but maybe she would like to see something different to compare
Yeah the dimensions of the card have changed :/
And now it doesn't look as good
So I said we could just use another printer, that has those dimensions
(The original ones that she was working with)
Fireball didn't do a great job w the business cards anyway so whatever
OMG!! is everything good with the baby so far? No problems?
Friday sounds good, I'll text you then
So cute right?! Weird and gross and also cute all at the same time. A strange combo!
Great. Text me then. Yup all is healthy and great so far and I feel far far better, though exhausted. Far less nauseous though, yay!
See I told you!! I'm so glad, you definitely need the energy for this business! Yay

I just remembered that design people (and Mechelle actually) used Moo to print their business cards. Its a great printer. More expensive but we are still working on the card anyway so maybe the money will push us to finalize a design we all love!
